{"tid":2253352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓接種流感疫苗後，死亡人數增至最少13人","createTime":"2020-10-22T05:53:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T06:36:22.000Z","uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"dc798347e28a8a7ba67b81ad5964510f0cfe194f","tid":2253352,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:53:28.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】南韓再有人接種流感疫苗後死亡，累計死亡人數增至最少13人。<br />\n<br />\n其中在慶尚北道有三名70歲以上的長者接種流感疫苗後死亡，大田市亦有一位70多歲的女性接種流感疫苗約三日後死亡。<br />\n<br />\n南韓至今有最少13人在接種流感疫苗後死亡，有人最短在接種後4小時死亡，最長則是接種後85小時。當局正在調查各人的死亡原因，但排除是疫苗導致，暫時不會暫停免費流感疫苗接種計劃。<br />\n<br />\n據報，所有死者接種的疫苗均是由南韓當地藥廠生產。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=410043\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D410043&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPYGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=6f97a189\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D410043&h=0e1c189d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=410043</a>"},{"pid":"008159c3702aac6483eadc8b27b10f89e2652dd8","tid":2253352,"uid":299433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:54:35.000Z","msg":"冇bot"},{"pid":"756a0a47d5c44c980531ddcadeba72544d4d87e3","tid":2253352,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"008159c3702aac6483eadc8b27b10f89e2652dd8","tid":2253352,"uid":299433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:54:35.000Z","msg":"冇bot"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:55:12.000Z","msg":"新人 ...<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec174017c431bd306abcec6705b120506c2cea05","tid":2253352,"uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T05:55:43.000Z","msg":"anti vaxxer wins"},{"pid":"d6580de1c39a9ffdb7c73b9ad4f60ea5826cf15c","tid":2253352,"u